le=\"color: gold;\">請緊記：「十點鐘，要鳩叫。」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我上面三件事都是不太需要成本的抗爭行為，而且能夠日常化。當每個人都願意走多一步，手足行動是能更有信心。手足願意為你冒險，你也願意為手足分擔一些風險嗎﹖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">總結：<br />\n1. 天氣冷，穿黑衣，能吸熱。<br />\n2. 空氣差，戴口罩。<br />\n3. 十點鐘，要鳩叫。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港，時代革命。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">五大訴求，缺一不可。</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:02:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xDDctJW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxDDctJW.png&h=9d8fc09a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2415dce3c7034bf78d70a1484f935fba316fa7c9","tid":1777762,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:16:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"432d8fe8839f30f622ce49e78a432f169071d03b","tid":1777762,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:17:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ffed56274c9373ca707193246cf3dcfd04a303ad","tid":1777762,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:20:17.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7e5e0df1f5c306031a9abc6309e54466045408af","tid":1777762,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:35:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1fad6b440ca7264a4be31e2109ac9f783f4eb7d0","tid":1777762,"uid":170297,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6a5df0804d33c206b0fd863012934af70e9eacaf","tid":1777762,"uid":74392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T13:02:48.000Z","msg":"sorry呢排唔記得戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n聽日開始會戴番"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:37:10.000Z","msg":"天氣凍更加要戴"},{"pid":"c02b56aab479feea0ae097e517d8adca8083be8a","tid":1777762,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:38:34.000Z","msg":"On9, 中共今次贏左，你連生活都唔會有，<br />\n睇下新彊<br />\n<br />\n當年64個時可能都有人話生活中抗爭，結果今日中國？"},{"pid":"20daa5ddc3e0d3b9e50f9e00fdf1d25bcf8eb01b","tid":1777762,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c02b56aab479feea0ae097e517d8adca8083be8a","tid":1777762,"uid":100016,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T14:38:34.000Z","msg":"On9, 中共今次贏左，你連生活都唔會有，<br />\n睇下新彊<br />\n<br />\n當年64個時可能都有人話生活中抗爭，結果今日中國？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T17:02:00.000Z","msg":"你講乜野？<br />\n我有話過唔和理非？<br />\n我有話過唔勇武？<br />\n我係講要一言一行都融入抗爭行動之中<br />\n你係唔識字定睇完標題就鳩屌？"},{"pid":"262acede1856f6b31755f5d3ce84110d2e63c852","tid":1777762,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T17:03:38.000Z","msg":"和理非最睇重成本效益, 以上既行動都低成本, 冇理由唔做"},{"pid":"d99654c633426847895c054b712ac555f738650d","tid":1777762,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T17:05:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e584240e61592134bf31a659d2ea9a0872fea0b7","tid":1777762,"uid":34217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T17:05:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"098f98690ce2ffc456d6eda21288b47138a0e343","tid":1777762,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T17:22:19.000Z","msg":"DGX 我覺得首國歌同進行曲可以進一步加長<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1778124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1778124</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"37b4d0f6538178bd3b9a88fd4c74a058589619cd","tid":1777762,"uid":169074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T17:23:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"15ba7bb75ca1c6ec25207ad14bdd5541931fadbb","tid":1777762,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-10T17:46:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bb0819948dd3ece1c33f11a7be39fe768237fa04","tid":1777762,"uid":273218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c0be49ea3fefc24d861be6327581ade9072bec6","tid":1777762,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dec94f51b